))), k = Nmin..Nmax)/(Nmax-Nmin+1);" }{MPLTEXT 1 -1 0 "" }}{PARA 239 "
> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 -1 15 "  rval[i] := r;" }{MPLTEXT 1 -1 0 "" }}
{PARA 225 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 7 "end do:" }{MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}
